parameters:
Villain: Hah hah... The time has finally come, Duke Shark!!
To be able to command you to do anything, what a wonderful
era we live in... All of us weaklings in the organization
have joined under the mayor's umbrella!!

Memimi: Ugh... Don't be deceived... Even if it seems good
now, Mayor Orca Broccoli... once he no longer needs you,
he'll easily cast you aside...

Villain: As long as it's good now, that's what matters!! My
sexual preferences are hard for others to understand... I
never thought I could satisfy them with you... Now, take off
your clothes!!
Memimi: Hii... Ah, ahh... Why do I have to... Noo...

Memimi: Uuu... You've fixed me face up... What are you
planning to do...? This position, with my legs raised...
It's all exposed... It's embarrassing...

Villain: Hah hah... What a nice pose!! The key to this play
is fixing both legs... Soon, being naked will be the least
of your worries as you beg me for mercy and scream in
tears!!

Henchman: Duke Shark has been fixed to the ground... His
ankles suspended... He's about to be tortured. It's pitiful,
but it also looks erotic...

Henchman: Is this some kind of SM play?! They say the toes
are full of nerves... I wonder how much Duke Shark can
endure...

Memimi: (I'm scared...! What is he planning to do... Even as
a villain, I hate pain... Someone help me...!)

Memimi: Eh, what!? My soles... Pffft, eh!? Eek! Ahh! Stop...
Ahahaha, what the...!

Memimi: Hii---!!? Ahahaha...! Gah, ah"! Ahee!!? Hahahaha,
ahahaha, ah"-----!!!

How childish... But it's funny to see Duke Shark being made
to laugh so disgracefully.

Henchman: No, but that must be tough... It's a respectable
form of torture I think... In its own way, it feels

Memimi: Eehh! Cough, cough... What are you doing... I can't
breathe... Tickling... Eh, really...?

Villain: Seeing a girl become completely confused from being
tickled excites me the most!! It's irresistible... Lose your

Memimi: Heeiiii! Ahahaha, hee! Heeii"i...! Wait, stop"!
Ahaha, just a moment"! Stop for a bit... Uhihihihihi! Can't

Memimi: Ahahaha, ahahh, guh, ah"ah"ah"ah"ah"!!! Heheheh…
Uu"hee"!! It's too much… Heh, ah, ahahaha, guh, n"n"n"!!

The villain persistently targets Memimi's soles with the
feather duster, giving her the exquisite sensation of barely
touching her. His skillful alternation of intensity is
something she can neither get used to nor endure; he won't
allow it...

Memimi: Heehii! Pfft… Heeii"i"i---!!! I give up"... Please

to cry from my tickling~?

Memimi: Not humiliated at all… Please, just stop", please…
Hiccup… Such a thing, I can't endure it… Uuu… Heeh… Heh,
heh...

Henchman: Duke Shark is begging for mercy…! If you're
tickled until you can't breathe, it's obviously too much… A

Villain: Uhehe… Quite the arousing plea but… After all,

Memimi: Gyaaaaaaaahahaha! It's "impossible", I "can't" take

ahahahahaha…! Oh" hee, ah", ahahaha…!

Villain: Tsk, tsk… I got so carried away that I made her wet

Villain: ...She's convulsing, but well, she should be
fine... I'll just remove the restraints and leave her be.
See ya, Duke Shark!

Until she woke up from fainting, Memimi continued to be
exposed in her miserable state, drenched in urine, to the
